name: T2DM_MedicationAllergyIntolerance
title: T2DM_Medication Allergy Intolerance
purpose: (Clinical Focus: SNOMED CT codes and RxNORM codes that could be returned by the FHIR Allergy Intolerance resource, and would indicate allergy or intolerance to T2 DM medications),(Data Element Scope: ALLERGY_INTOLERANCE:),(Inclusion Criteria: RxNORM codes for individual medications that are T2 DM medications, and various SNOMED CT codes that would indicate allergy or intolerance to T2 DM medications as a class, or individual T2 DM medications),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
